{"tid":1955975,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【預算案】林鄭年薪521萬元全球第二高 去年加自己人工12萬元","createTime":"2020-04-03T00:36:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-03T06:15:14.000Z","uid":130626,"like":4,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"69fad872d9de6b472b3ef433d46906d16a8fa528","tid":1955975,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T00:36:59.000Z","msg":"特首林鄭月娥年薪去年已逾500萬元，是全球薪酬第二高的領導人，今年再「加人工」。公民黨立法會議員陳淑莊就《財政預算案》向特首辦查詢，獲覆林鄭月娥的年薪為521萬元，較去年度509萬元增加12萬元，即平均每月加薪1萬元，另外非實報實銷酬酢津貼為98.2萬元。新民黨立法會議員容海恩則問特首會否自願減薪，以展示管治團隊與市民同心抗疫、共渡時艱。<br />\n<br />\n行政長官辦公室覆稱，本年2月底行政長官及整個問責團隊向公益金捐出1個月薪酬，希望能夠幫助社會上有需要的人士，「往後如情況繼續轉差，問責團隊會作出適時回應。」<br />\n<br />\n根據美國財經網站「24/7 Wall S」去年統計，全球年薪最高的領導人為新加坡總理李顯龍，約1,255萬港元。林鄭月娥居次，比美國總統特朗普、澳洲總理莫里森、德國總理默克爾等西方領袖的年薪更高。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200403/large/1585848545_6895.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200403%2Flarge%2F1585848545_6895.png&h=c40abeee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200403/F7EWSI366SE2QEPKEOUVX7MZAM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200403%2FF7EWSI366SE2QEPKEOUVX7MZAM%2F&d=M80n4YL9TfmCcvG0giRsMoV%2FGdaNkEJkjxlYCjQUfm8%3D&h=7e5ceb20\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200403%2FF7EWSI366SE2QEPKEOUVX7MZAM%2F&h=c6a9f479\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200403/F7EWSI366SE2QEPKEOUVX7MZAM/</a>"},{"pid":"01f193ef015ae58631c391b23ef4561327dd29ad","tid":1955975,"uid":55089,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T00:38:20.000Z","msg":"痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"156c1e9ab844bee1cb6675df8ce925a6164a1150","tid":1955975,"uid":125168,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T00:38:40.000Z","msg":"應該同雜種睇齊"},{"pid":"5c2c